pfSense-pkg-speedtest integrates the Ookla Speedtest CLI into the pfSense
web GUI, providing on-demand and scheduled internet speed testing directly
from the Services menu. Results include download speed, upload speed, ping
latency, and jitter, along with Ookla server information. Up to 14 historical
results are retained and displayed in a sortable table.

This package requires acceptance of the Ookla End User License Agreement
(https://www.speedtest.net/about/eula) and Privacy Policy before running tests.
